hits.shortDescription:
Treat your leather to some TLC. Specially formulated for Coach, Coach Leather Moisturizer extends the natural life and beauty of our leathers while preserving each leather's unique character. Regular use will help preserve both the leather's suppleness and color. For best results, we recommend pairing with our Coach Leather Cleaner.

To preserve the beauty of Coach leather over time, we recommend regular cleaning and conditioning every three months.

plpSeoBottomContent:
You’ve got (a lot) of options.
Designer handbags, purses, crossbody bags, tote bags, backpacks, shoulder bags, satchels, clutches, belt bags…you get the idea. We’ve got women’s purses for every outfit, activity and occasion. Because getting dressed is about more than just fashion—it’s about expressing yourself.

Find a bag that’s just your style.
Need help finding the perfect designer bag? You’ve come to the right place.
Heading to work?You might want a timeless tote bag to hold your laptop, notebook and an extra pair of shoes for later. Going out with friends? Make a major impression with an on-trend box bag or mini crossbody that holds your keys, cards and an extra lipstick (or two).
And remember: we’ve got wallets that match with (and fit inside) every silhouette.

More about our marvelous materials.
What sets Coach handbags and purses above the rest? Materials that are crafted to last—like Original Glovetanned Leather, buttery-soft suede, smooth Sport Calf leather, Signature Jaquard, and more.


We even upcycle our leather scraps to create brand-new woven leathers that reflect our ongoing commitment to rethinking and reducing our impact on the planet. It feels good, in more ways than one.


Don’t forget the little things. (We sure don’t.)
Like the details that make our everyday handbags extraordinary. From hand-applied embellishments to perfectly sized pockets, you’ll be able to see (and feel) what sets us apart from the rest.


One thing that all of our bags have in common? A Storypatch on the inside. Each is marked with a unique registration number for its style—symbolizing the authenticity of Coach products (and proving yet again that it’s what’s on the inside that counts).
And, a little bit about us, too. (In case you didn’t know.)


Coach is a global fashion house founded in New York in 1941. Inspired by the vision of Creative Director Stuart Vevers and the inclusive and courageous spirit of our hometown, we make beautiful things, crafted to last—for you to be yourself in.
If you ever need help picking out a leather purse…or wallet…or jacket (or just want to chat), text an in-store stylist at +1 503-455-5777. Monday–Friday, 11am–9pm EST. We’d love to help.
